At this point of time, only one operator parameter in Content by Label macro is allowed. User can only choose one of *AND* or *OR* operator. 

With this said, advanced logical expression functionality could not be done.

{code}
(label1 AND label2) OR (label3 AND (label4 OR label5) )
{code}

