The documentation on [Confluence Storage Format|https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/AOD/Confluence+Storage+Format] for Atlassian OnDemand states:

{quote}
If you would like to edit the storage format for a page, your Confluence system administrator will need to install the Confluence Source Editor plugin.
{quote}

However, the [Confluence Source Editor plugin|https://marketplace.atlassian.com/plugins/com.atlassian.confluence.plugins.editor.confluence-source-editor] is not available for Atlassian OnDemand.

Please edit the documentation to reflect only what is available for Atlassian OnDemand.

Cheers,
Jeison Spaniol
